{"id":171692,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011811/","date":"2011-08-11T21:30:26Z","modified":"2011-08-11T21:30:26Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/8/11","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/artanddesign/2011/aug/10/ai-weiwei-chinese-police\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">艾未未被控偷税而被关押</span>81<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">天，消息人士透露了他被关押的一些细</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">节</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约客》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/evanosnos/2011/08/ai-weiwei-drawn-into-the-vortex-of-politics.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国来信——艾未未“被卷进政治漩涡”</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《大西洋月刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2011/09/arab-spring-chinese-winter/8601/?single_page=true\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">阿拉伯之春，中国之冬</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在阿拉伯人民的抗争之后，中国也有大事出现：政府发动了近年来最大规模的对异议人士的打击</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/09/us-china-xinjiang-idUSTRE7781FG20110809?feedType=RSS&#038;feedName=worldNews&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:%20reuters/worldNews%20(News%20/%20US%20/%20International)\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">喀什的征地活动为维吾尔人的愤怒火上浇油</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在内地司空见惯的社会问题，到边疆就会带上民族色彩</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">黎明新闻：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.dawn.com/2011/08/10/five-chinese-nationals-deported.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">巴基斯坦遣返无名中国籍新疆分裂主义人士</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——包括一名妇女和两名孩子</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博新闻社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-11/china-banning-u-s-professors-elicits-silence-from-colleges.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国禁止美国教授入境，美国大学无动于衷</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span>13</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">位来自美国大学的教授因为《新疆：中国的穆斯林边疆》一书而受到中国打压，但他们所在的学院对此却保持沉默</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110811/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_bullet_train\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国高速火车制造商暂停部分生产活动</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——长春铁路机车厂对生产活动进行整顿</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/08/11/chinas-high-speed-rail-woes/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的高铁烦恼</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国暂停审批新高铁、铁路降速、安全检查、机车制造商整顿，中国的高铁麻烦不少</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社分析：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110810/ts_nm/us_economy_china\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国是否成了信用危机的买单人？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——最大的债权人，可能也是债务危机的最大受害者</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/panosmourdoukoutas/2011/08/09/a-tale-of-two-inflations-in-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的通胀分两类</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——商品通胀</span></span><span><span>7</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月达到</span></span><span><span>6.5%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，而房地产通胀则达到</span></span><span><span>11.7%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业内幕》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/made-in-china-money-goes-to-america-2011-8?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+businessinsider+%28Business+Insider%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国制造，钱归美国</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——当你购买中国制造的产品时，你的钱大多流向美国</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国听说博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinahearsay.com/china-exports-are-up-and-why-you-shouldnt-care/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国出口增加，但你不用操心</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——三个理由你不用害怕廉价的中国进口货</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">雅虎</span></span><span><span>/</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110811/ap_on_re_as/as_china_tainted_food\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在瘦肉精事件中，中国再逮捕</span>7<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">位嫌疑犯</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-10/china-government-to-suspend-approvals-on-rail-projects-after-deadly-crash.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国政府下令停止新铁路项目：铁路股下跌，航空股上涨</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110811/wl_nm/us_china_power_shortages\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国电力官员说，接下来仍将做好</span>“<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">最坏准备</span>”</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，保证其电网能够满足创纪录的电力需</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">求</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2087973,00.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一滩浑水：为什么中国海军新航母让亚洲邻国不安</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/08/10/riot_of_opportunity\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">伦敦骚乱给国际批评者提供了机会</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——利比亚发言人称，卡梅隆失去了合法性，该走人了；人民日报评西方支持互联网自由，这次吃到了苦果；新华社担心伦敦奥运会的安全</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/11/us-britain-riot-iran-idUSTRE77A11420110811?feedType=RSS&#038;feedName=topNews&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+reuters%2FtopNews+%28News+%2F+US+%2F+Top+News%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">英国回应伊朗，愿意与之讨论人权，及如何应对街头骚</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">乱</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《基督教科学箴言报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.csmonitor.com/World/terrorism-security/2011/0810/London-riots-push-British-leaders-to-approve-harsher-police-tactics-VIDEO?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:+feeds/world+(Christian+Science+Monitor+%7C+World)&#038;utm_content=Googl\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">英国公众问为什么政府迟迟未能授权警察使用橡皮子弹等武器对待暴徒</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/aug/11/north-korea-denies-firing-south\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北朝鲜否认和韩国交火</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。指责韩国好战分子对建筑爆破</span></span><span><span>“</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">过度反应</span></span><span><span>”</span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/11/nyregion/chinese-investment-grows-in-new-york-city.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rssnyt\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国大笔投资纽约</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">城</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/financialcrisis/8694272/UK-growth-is-now-in-Chinas-hands.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">英国的增长攥在中国手里</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——世界的命运都被中国和德国的决策者所掌握了</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：中国官方学者撰文指出，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://online.wsj.com/article/BT-CO-20110810-722889.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国应抓住目前全球金融市场动荡时机，推动汇率灵活</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">性</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/11/china-economy-forex-idUSL3E7JB02U20110811\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国央行报纸引述本地银行人士称，中国应加快外汇储备多样化</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；买入更多日元或欧元资</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">产</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-11/china-s-yuan-strengthens-beyond-6-40-per-dollar-for-first-time-since-1993.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">人民币对美元汇率升至</span>17<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年高点</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，表明中国将用汇率来帮助处理通</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">胀</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：为筹资，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/10/us-bankofamerica-china-idUSTRE77978020110810\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">洲</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">银行正在和科威特卡塔尔主要投资基金展开试探性会谈，出售其持有的中国建设银行股票</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：中投公司出资</span></span><span><span>23<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/09/gdfsuez-china-board-idUSWEA972920110809\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿欧元，购买法国燃气苏伊士集团勘探和生产公司</span>30%<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">股份</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，据称将有助于后者扩大亚太业务</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-10/hacker-attack-on-hong-kong-exchange-website-triggers-halts.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">港交所网站被黑客攻击，部分交易被迫暂</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">停</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/08/11/near-death-experiences-getting-sick-in-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">濒死体验——我在中国的生病经历</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/11/world/asia/11taiwan.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rssnyt\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对许多大陆游客而言，</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">台湾的文化影响有限</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他们最大的惊奇是，大多数台湾人对统一并不热衷</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia-pacific/a-showdown-over-traditional-throat-singing-divides-china-and-mongolia/2011/06/24/gIQASaZS7I_story.html?wprss=rss_asia-pacific\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国和</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">蒙古在传统喉音唱法上分歧严重</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——蒙古老师教会了中国学生，但中国却把它申请了世界遗产</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>友情提示：译者Podcast已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；需翻墙更新下载。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-6508326417864683644?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":139,"categories":[1],"tags":[9282,13769]}